10. Electric Vehicle Fleet Coordinator
GreenMove Transport Solutions
Locations: Cebu City, Lapu-Lapu City
GreenMove Transport Solutions operates the largest electric jeepney fleet in Cebu with 45 units currently in service. We're modernizing public transportation while reducing carbon emissions and providing better working conditions for drivers.
JOB SUMMARY: Coordinate daily operations of our electric vehicle fleet including charging schedules, maintenance, driver assignments, and route optimization.
WHAT YOU'LL DO:

Schedule vehicle charging and ensure optimal battery health management
Coordinate preventive maintenance and repairs with service providers
Monitor vehicle performance data and identify operational issues
Manage driver schedules and ensure regulatory compliance
Track energy consumption and cost metrics
Work with local transport regulators on franchise compliance

REQUIREMENTS:

Bachelor's degree in Business Administration, Logistics, or Engineering
2+ years in fleet management or transport operations
Basic understanding of electric vehicle technology
Strong organizational and problem-solving abilities
Valid driver's license (Restriction Code 1,2,3)

Job Type: Full-time